i18n.untranslatedContent: Agbur-agi ur yella ara s tutlayt-ik/im.

messages.automaticMessage: Ixef-agi yettusuqel s wudem awurman seg tespanyulit. Ur yettwasenqed ara sɣur umdan. Ma tebɣiḍ ad talleleḍ deg usenqed, nermes-aɣ-d s usiti dagi.
messages.originalMessage: Agbur n yixef-agi yebna ɣef uḍris amezwaru n tespanyulit.
messages.revisedMessage: Ixef-agi yettwaseqed sɣur umdan yerna yettusuqel seg uḍris amezwaru n tespanyulit. Ma yella mazal yeḥwaǧ aseɣti, nermes-aɣ-d s usiti dagi.

page.draft: Agbur-agi d arewway yerna ur yettili ara deg lebni n useɣẓan.
search.devWarning:
Anadi yella kan deg lebni n useɣẓan. 
Ɛreḍ ad tebnuḍ neɣ ad twaliḍ asmel i wakken ad t-tɛerḍeḍ deg umḍiq-ik.
